# Abstract {.unnumbered}

This is a report summarising the knowledge gained about seabird space use through 9 years of SEATRACK (Phase I and II). It details the spatio-temporal distribution of seabirds inhabiting the North Atlantic, including areas used by birds breeding in Norway and the composition of birds inhabiting the Norwegian ocean management areas.
